{"tid":1332112,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"李偲嫣勾結外國勢力","createTime":"2019-07-19T07:43:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-19T07:47:21.000Z","uid":281070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6580fd0a925879b1dd7e95f1a563dc39c653e658","tid":1332112,"uid":281070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T07:43:12.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">市民到警總贈送1萬包檸檬茶和紀念牌 感謝警方執法</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n大約20名市民到灣仔警察總部外，贈送1萬包檸檬茶及紀念牌予香港警方，感謝警察嚴正執法。參與者包括<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins>新加坡香港商會</ins></span></strong>及香港正義聯盟代表。在場人士手持「香港警察 愛國愛港」等標語。警方派代表接受紀念牌。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins><strong>新加坡香港商會會長陳文平</strong></ins></span>說，不容許示威者破壞香港法治、美化暴力的情況出現，指戴口罩的示威者是沒承擔的行為。<br />\n<br />\n香港正義聯盟主席李偲嫣提出4項訴求，包括定性6.12衝突事件為暴動、希望警務處處長盧偉聰能給予適當指揮，使前線人員免受傷害、處理立法會議員在示威期間阻礙警方執法問題，及成立特別小組展開調查，拘捕涉事分子。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1469218-20190719.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1469218-20190719.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=iVbTvSvdcfz%2Fe2yCQDPMVxTmJET03dBbukdTSFliYCA%3D&h=00a6a32a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1469218-20190719.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=9aae529a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1469218-20190719.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n來源 : 香港電台新聞"},{"pid":"12e972edfde7a0277e6aa6fb6682c3633aa7e651","tid":1332112,"uid":238051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T07:45:33.000Z","msg":"【有人冒警】面對冒警情境練習場<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1332100\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1332100</a><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">有人冒警\n你扮警察\n冇委任證\n涉嫌傷人\n藏有攻擊性武器\n我地行使公民逮捕權</code></pre>"},{"pid":"7af95b79f8fd1ae245e6ae2253b9c84b816ad408","tid":1332112,"uid":8762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T07:47:21.000Z","msg":"外國勢力喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n口交部唔出聲？<br />\n藍絲又唔出聲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}